==English==
===Etymology===
See the Wikipedia article [[w:ISO 216|ISO 216]], the international standard on paper sizes.

===Noun===
'''A7'''
# A standard [[paper]] size, defined by ISO 216.
#: dimensions: 105 x 74 mm  (105.112 x 74.325 mm)
# The seventh address register on [[Motorola]] [[68k]] processors.

===Adjective===
'''A7'''
# of that size
#:  ''a sheet of '''A7''' paper''

